I know it's gonk, it's just... I miss him. A lot.

I guess you made a bigger impression than you thought.

His favorite.

He said the guy who wrote it was tougher than Morgan Blackhand.

I think he mighta been the first kid to ditch the Valentinos.
Like Jackie?

Dante's captain of the NC Blackouts now.

Why'd he hold onto it?
Old school ganger. Valentinos, of course.
No, I only ever heard about him. But he didn't exactly inspire many fond memories.
Yeah. Best darn year of my life.
You actually got to know him – the real Jackie. Everybody else thought he was a goofball with a rough-hewn face and an edge. But they're wrong.
He said they're collectibles. They don't print them anymore.

Part of the strategic reserve?

A man – with dreams, ambitions. Only thing they cost him was his life.

Come on.
